  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/085da986828205b01018786bc78aba87.poster.avif?t=1764148960\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/085da986828205b01018786bc78aba87.webm?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/085da986828205b01018786bc78aba87.mp4?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The beautiful planet Regilus, with its breathtakingly diverse ecosystem, has been targeted by various colonizers over the years. Eventually, however, the Teleportation Travel Agencies took over the planet, turning it into one of the most desirable tourist attractions in the galaxy. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/d339ec9b8d9e72f48c97671e1da94255.poster.avif?t=1764148960\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/d339ec9b8d9e72f48c97671e1da94255.webm?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/d339ec9b8d9e72f48c97671e1da94255.mp4?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>However, when Amia and Bogard arrive planetside to start their dream vacation adventure, they discover they’ve been separated and landed nowhere close to the hotel they were travelling to. With their suspicious guide's help, Amia and Bogard need to set off on a journey full of logical puzzles and tricky riddles on seven unique maps. Will they be able to solve this planet's mystery?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/b8da51a6a7e9f162072b66f94c2d4163.poster.avif?t=1764148960\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/b8da51a6a7e9f162072b66f94c2d4163.webm?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/b8da51a6a7e9f162072b66f94c2d4163.mp4?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game's creator and puzzle designer is the legendary Roland Pantoła – creator of critically acclaimed classic titles such as AD 2044, Reah and the Schizm series. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/4c312b8622b8061811ca8995ae993a6f.poster.avif?t=1764148960\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/4c312b8622b8061811ca8995ae993a6f.webm?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/4c312b8622b8061811ca8995ae993a6f.mp4?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple difficulty levels to customize your experience;<br></li><li>First-person investigation-based gameplay;<br></li><li>7 different maps with varying biomes;<br></li><li>Unique story keeping you in suspense until the end;<br></li><li>A variety of puzzles and riddles created by Roland Pantoła;<br></li><li>A digital guide to help you out if you get stuck.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/085da986828205b01018786bc78aba87.poster.avif?t=1764148960\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/085da986828205b01018786bc78aba87.webm?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/085da986828205b01018786bc78aba87.mp4?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The beautiful planet Regilus, with its breathtakingly diverse ecosystem, has been targeted by various colonizers over the years. Eventually, however, the Teleportation Travel Agencies took over the planet, turning it into one of the most desirable tourist attractions in the galaxy. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/d339ec9b8d9e72f48c97671e1da94255.poster.avif?t=1764148960\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/d339ec9b8d9e72f48c97671e1da94255.webm?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/d339ec9b8d9e72f48c97671e1da94255.mp4?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>However, when Amia and Bogard arrive planetside to start their dream vacation adventure, they discover they’ve been separated and landed nowhere close to the hotel they were travelling to. With their suspicious guide's help, Amia and Bogard need to set off on a journey full of logical puzzles and tricky riddles on seven unique maps. Will they be able to solve this planet's mystery?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/b8da51a6a7e9f162072b66f94c2d4163.poster.avif?t=1764148960\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/b8da51a6a7e9f162072b66f94c2d4163.webm?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/b8da51a6a7e9f162072b66f94c2d4163.mp4?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game's creator and puzzle designer is the legendary Roland Pantoła – creator of critically acclaimed classic titles such as AD 2044, Reah and the Schizm series. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/4c312b8622b8061811ca8995ae993a6f.poster.avif?t=1764148960\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/4c312b8622b8061811ca8995ae993a6f.webm?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/986350/extras/4c312b8622b8061811ca8995ae993a6f.mp4?t=1764148960\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multiple difficulty levels to customize your experience;<br></li><li>First-person investigation-based gameplay;<br></li><li>7 different maps with varying biomes;<br></li><li>Unique story keeping you in suspense until the end;<br></li><li>A variety of puzzles and riddles created by Roland Pantoła;<br></li><li>A digital guide to help you out if you get stuck.</li></ul>",
